{"ProductId":"290","Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Sleek – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ShortDescription":"Minimalist frames and slim horizontal windows for bright, unobstructed views","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/avante-az-595.webp?sfvrsn=70ef6b44_10","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avantesleek","Overview":"<h3>Next-Level Garage Door Design</h3><h4>Premium Aluminum Frame</h4><p>The Avante&reg; Sleek is crafted from tough, 2-1/8\" commercial-grade aluminum that won&rsquo;t rust or warp, so you get lasting strength with a refined look.</p><h4>Light-Filled Options</h4><p>Choose from clear, frosted, tinted, or obscure tempered glass&mdash;or even acrylic panels&mdash;to let in as much light (and privacy) as you want.</p><h4>Custom Finishes</h4><p>Pick from classic anodized or painted finishes, go bold with powder-coat colors, or match your home perfectly with over 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg;</a> options.</p><h4>Insulated for Comfort</h4><p>Select models include <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation</a> and insulated glass to help keep your garage more comfortable, year-round.</p><h4>Wind-Ready Protection</h4><p>Ask about our <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> to meet code in high-wind areas.</p><h4>C-Power&trade; Technology</h4><p>Our <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/c-power-technology\">Click-to-Conceal&trade; panels</a> can instantly transition from transparent to opaque with the tap of a remote, providing on-demand visual privacy without sacrificing the door&rsquo;s architectural aesthetic.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul type=\"disc\"><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li><li>Meets ASHRAE&reg; 90.1 Title 24 and IECC&reg; (International Energy Conservation Code) 2021 Section C406.9 Air Infiltration requirements.</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>Solid Construction for Everyday Confidence</h3><p>The Avante&reg; Sleek garage door is built to look great and stand the test of time. Its frame is made from commercial-grade aluminum, so it&rsquo;s naturally rust-resistant and practically maintenance-free&mdash;just an occasional rinse keeps it looking fresh.</p><p>For added comfort, select models feature Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation in the rails and stiles, helping keep your garage quieter and more comfortable. Every panel is joined with a weather-sealing section joint, so rain and wind stay outside where they belong. Also, an integral reinforcing fin adds extra strength and stability on wider doors.</p><p>You can choose from a wide variety of glass or acrylic panel options to get the perfect combination of light, privacy, and style for your home.</p><div class=\"options-container\"><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-avanteax-1l-non-tg.webp?sfvrsn=621b921_1\" alt=\"Avante Construction\" sf-size=\"3022\" /><div>Model AZ6 made of 2-1/8&rdquo; durable commercial grade aluminum, making it virtually maintenance-free and long-lasting</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-avanteaxu.webp?sfvrsn=b2614212_1\" alt=\"Avante Construction\" sf-size=\"2816\" /><div>Model AZ6U made of 2-1/8\" durable commercial grade aluminum with <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg;</a> polyurethane insulation with an R-value of 3.8 (with clear insulated glass)</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/avante-ax-section-jointafbb6bf6-aae4-46fe-bfd2-9d85bb40efc2.webp?sfvrsn=7123d472_2\" alt=\"Section Joint\" sf-size=\"4196\" /><div>Integral section joint seal for further reduction of air and water infiltration</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/avante-ax-frame-detail.webp?sfvrsn=c8ced87e_1\" alt=\"Avante Construction\" sf-size=\"1506\" /><div>Smooth flat frame edge design for a more contemporary look</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/avante-ax-section-joint01.webp?sfvrsn=ba3d07b5_1\" alt=\"Section Joint\" sf-size=\"5242\" /><div>Reinforcing fin included on doors wider than 14&rsquo;. Standard doors 12&rsquo; and under do not use built-in reinforcing fin. Usage on widths 12&rsquo;2&rdquo; to 14&rsquo; depend upon glass weight. WindCode&reg; doors may vary.</div></div><div class=\"commerical-image-fixed-width-large\"><div><strong></strong>For Avante&reg; Sleek doors equipped with our innovative and new <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/c-power-technology\">C-Power&trade; Technology</a>, all wiring is concealed within the door sections for a clean appearance and simple installation.</div></div></div><h2 class=\"h3\">Additional Features</h2><ul><li>Replaceable vinyl bottom weather seal in a rust-resistant aluminum retainer helps keep out air and water.</li><li>Integral section joint seal helps keep out air and water. </li><li>Built-in reinforcing fin provides increased strength and longevity. Included on doors wider than 14&rsquo;. Standard doors 12&rsquo; and under do not use a reinforcing fin. Usage on doors 12&rsquo;2&rdquo; to 14&rsquo; wide depends upon glass weight. <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg;</a> doors may vary.</li><li>A patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg; prevents serious injury that could occur if the bottom bracket were removed with the garage door closed and under tension</li><li>All <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg;</a> insulated doors come standard with 10-ball nylon rollers and heavy-duty 14-gauge steel hinges.</li></ul>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Avante Sleek","DisplayIndex":10,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/avante-sleek","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>The Avante&reg; Sleek lets you choose a finish that fits your style, whether you want something classic or bold. Go for the clean, modern look of Clear Aluminum (anodized), Standard White, rich Chocolate, or one of several shades of Bronze and Black, available in both anodized and painted finishes. If you love the look of bronze but want a consistent color throughout, the Bronze (painted) option is your best bet.</p><p>You can also customize your door with Clopay&rsquo;s Color Blast&reg; paint system or RAL powder coat finishes&mdash;over 1,500 colors available. These finishes are designed to stand up to the elements and keep your door looking sharp for years.</p><p><em>Note: Due to the anodizing process, color variation may occur. The use of Bronze (Painted)&rdquo; is recommended for a more consistent bronze finish\r\n        color. Custom colors available.</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>The Avante&reg; Sleek keeps\r\n    things streamlined, right down to the hardware. Every door comes with the\r\n    option to add sleek, color-matched aluminum grip handles that blend perfectly\r\n    with your chosen frame color. These handles are built for comfort and easy use,\r\n    making it simple to open and close your door every day.<o:p></o:p></p>","DesignDisclaimer":"<p><em>*Only available on doors equipped with C-Power&reg; technology. Glass available in insulated tempered or laminated.</em></p><p>Please note hardcoated options are available.<strong></strong></p>","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Modern Steel™","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/modern-steel-flush_fullview-window-black-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=db7014e9_14","Id":"170","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/modern-steel-collection","DisplayIndex":7,"ShortDescription":"Subtle modern beauty, simple up-keep","AlternativeText":"Modern Steel"},{"Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/tnahcpower01showcase.webp?sfvrsn=e1a1ed6c_1","Id":"16","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avante","DisplayIndex":9,"ShortDescription":"Aluminum and glass doors that make your garage a stunning focal point, providing natural light by day and a dramatic glow at night","AlternativeText":"Avante"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Avante Sleek Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-avanteazss-22.webp?sfvrsn=993295d9_3","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-AVANTEAZSS-22.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Products Available Through Independent Dealers","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/idea-book.webp?sfvrsn=699cfb64_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-IMAGINE-14.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2}],"ProductInstallationAndCare":[{"Title":"Installation Instructions for Avan